<p><br><br>盒子跟遥控器。<br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//2265/22655a45379457f73cac3bd9a3f07011.com/large/18b100058735c1c52507"><br><br>正面，有三颗指示灯。<br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//e283/e28396a5050a41d7e84fc2d610a3c1d9.com/large/191600035434e5f5eae8"><br><br>侧面，两个2.0的USB接口，网上有这个型号的是3.0跟2.0各一个，但是我的这个是两个2.0的，应该是缩水版。<br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//0084/0084ccb5d64746e16d44c574160f6209.com/large/191800037f1ef85495ec"><br><br>另一侧，可以插TF卡。<br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//0d96/0d96be48f8609d39646493e5b6b716f8.com/large/191600035430d651b0c6"><br><br>背面接口，功能还是挺多的，HDMIAV 光纤 网络接口都有。<br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//80a9/80a95c5646d0e976acabfc34c538c008.com/large/191500037d8809ecdb65"><br><br>背面。<br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//9fef/9fef3717e71ab35c33a175440e564b02.com/large/191a00037b9232883df5"><br><br>拆开后，天线贴在上盖上的，很不方便，线又不能拆。<br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//a527/a52713dfdc0f2770bcf7a7514d1ebffd.com/large/191800037f1cd9bb8fb9"><br><br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//ace8/ace848dfef80f3c356df8152a8c490d1.com/large/19160003542baade249c"><br><br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//6c75/6c751e56e1ddcf9a37cdc5fe7a2b0017.com/large/191b000352f7316d088e"><br><br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//6b02/6b02a20c9f129afd9fd119ac3ed2eac5.com/large/191500037d8241bc6687"><br><br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//134a/134acd12bcd641081090232ee00d9505.com/large/191800037f1981511c03"><br><br>TLL接有了，不用焊针了。<br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//d69e/d69e45dd23bc0bde57a15be46d289b27.com/large/19160003542688130de2"><br><br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//e089/e0890a52290a410b76c18fb915b145d5.com/large/191a00037b81ee92092f"><br><br>底盒，没有配重块，拿在手上很轻。<br><br><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//a4a6/a4a6b9b8caf5f096102a8014d0f4ac3d.com/large/191800037f1741ee624c"></p> 
